mapproperties.key: This simulation mimics the patients and her caregivers daily activities as described in the interview.
This simulation tries to mimic the patients troubles when moving. All move actions are delayed by 50%

This simulation focuses on the reported pain the patient has in the lower back area. The filter this time is in the form of an out loud message. When performing tasks such as walking, getting in and out of bed or sitting in a chair the agent has a 30% chance of complaining about her pain.
This simulation combines the previous two symptoms but as a whole. The patient has movement problems and sometimes compains about her lower back pain.
